.IP \[bu] 2
\f[C]<address>\f[]
.RS 2
.PP
Defaults to the address specified in the provided flash image file.
.RE
.IP \[bu] 2
\f[C]<length>\f[]
.RS 2
.PP
Defaults to length of the data in the provided image file.
.RE
